    skos:altLabel "MIxS-BE (built environment)" ;
    skos:definition "A collection of terms appropriate when collecting samples and sequencing samples obtained in the built-up environment, which includes terms for surface material, humidity, temperature, moisture and occupancy type along with specific metadata terms describing the indoor air, building and sample properties." ;
