    skos:altLabel "MIxS-HCR (hydrocarbon resources-fluids/swabs)" ;
    skos:definition "A collection of terms appropriate when collecting samples and sequencing samples obtained from environments pertaining to hydrocarbon resources, specifically run-off liquids samples and swabs." ;
    MIXS:use_cases "The microbial characterization of hydrocarbon occurrences,  defined as the natural and artificial environmental features that are rich in hydrocarbons, from hydrocarbon resource fluids." .

