    skos:altLabel "MIxS-Food (animal and animal feed)" ;
    skos:definition "A collection of terms appropriate when collecting samples and performing sequencing of samples obtained from farm animals and their feed." ;
    skos:note "This extension is intended to work alongside the other food extensions (farm environment, food production facility, and human foods) for capturing contextual data across the food supply-chain environment." ;
    MIXS:use_cases "Microbiome of farm animals, their feed, and pet food." .

