    skos:altLabel "MIxS-Food(food production facility)" ;
    skos:definition "A collection of terms appropriate when collecting samples and performing sequencing of samples obtained from food production facilities." ;
    skos:note "This extension is intended to work alongside the other food extensions (animals and animal feed, farm environment, and human foods) for capturing contextual data across the food supply-chain environment." ;
    MIXS:use_cases "Microbiome of food production facilities/factories" .

