    skos:altLabel "MIxS-Food (human foods)" ;
    skos:definition "A collection of terms appropriate when collecting samples and performing sequencing of samples obtained from human food products." ;
    skos:note "This extension is intended to work alongside the other food extensions (animals and animal feed, farm environment, and food production facilities) for capturing contextual data across the food supply-chain environment." ;
    MIXS:use_cases "Microbiome of foods intended for human consumption." .

