    owl:unionOf ( <https://w3id.org/mixs/SurfMaterialEnum#adobe> <https://w3id.org/mixs/SurfMaterialEnum#carpet> <https://w3id.org/mixs/SurfMaterialEnum#cinder%20blocks> <https://w3id.org/mixs/SurfMaterialEnum#concrete> <https://w3id.org/mixs/SurfMaterialEnum#glass> <https://w3id.org/mixs/SurfMaterialEnum#hay%20bales> <https://w3id.org/mixs/SurfMaterialEnum#metal> <https://w3id.org/mixs/SurfMaterialEnum#paint> <https://w3id.org/mixs/SurfMaterialEnum#plastic> <https://w3id.org/mixs/SurfMaterialEnum#stainless%20steel> <https://w3id.org/mixs/SurfMaterialEnum#stone> <https://w3id.org/mixs/SurfMaterialEnum#stucco> <https://w3id.org/mixs/SurfMaterialEnum#tile> <https://w3id.org/mixs/SurfMaterialEnum#vinyl> <https://w3id.org/mixs/SurfMaterialEnum#wood> ) ;
    linkml:permissible_values <https://w3id.org/mixs/SurfMaterialEnum#adobe>,
        <https://w3id.org/mixs/SurfMaterialEnum#carpet>,
        <https://w3id.org/mixs/SurfMaterialEnum#cinder%20blocks>,
        <https://w3id.org/mixs/SurfMaterialEnum#concrete>,
        <https://w3id.org/mixs/SurfMaterialEnum#glass>,
