    owl:unionOf ( <https://w3id.org/mixs/GeolAgeEnum#Archean> <https://w3id.org/mixs/GeolAgeEnum#Cambrian> <https://w3id.org/mixs/GeolAgeEnum#Carboniferous> <https://w3id.org/mixs/GeolAgeEnum#Cenozoic> <https://w3id.org/mixs/GeolAgeEnum#Cretaceous> <https://w3id.org/mixs/GeolAgeEnum#Devonian> <https://w3id.org/mixs/GeolAgeEnum#Jurassic> <https://w3id.org/mixs/GeolAgeEnum#Mesozoic> <https://w3id.org/mixs/GeolAgeEnum#Neogene> <https://w3id.org/mixs/GeolAgeEnum#Ordovician> <https://w3id.org/mixs/GeolAgeEnum#Paleogene> <https://w3id.org/mixs/GeolAgeEnum#Paleozoic> <https://w3id.org/mixs/GeolAgeEnum#Permian> <https://w3id.org/mixs/GeolAgeEnum#Precambrian> <https://w3id.org/mixs/GeolAgeEnum#Proterozoic> <https://w3id.org/mixs/GeolAgeEnum#Silurian> <https://w3id.org/mixs/GeolAgeEnum#Triassic> <https://w3id.org/mixs/GeolAgeEnum#other> ) ;
