        <https://w3id.org/mixs/GeolAgeEnum#Cenozoic>,
        <https://w3id.org/mixs/GeolAgeEnum#Cretaceous>,
        <https://w3id.org/mixs/GeolAgeEnum#Devonian>,
        <https://w3id.org/mixs/GeolAgeEnum#Jurassic>,
        <https://w3id.org/mixs/GeolAgeEnum#Mesozoic>,
